<p><strong>14-1.</strong> deploy가 완료되면 위와 같이 Team wiki tile, Application endpoints, Commit history, Continuous deployment, Application activity등이 나타납니다. <br /></p>
<figure>
  <img src="http://labs.brandi.co.kr///assets/2018/20180209/21.png" alt="21" style="border:1px solid #ccc;" />
